Comparing the 7-day averages of daily confirmed cases from the past 7 days and those from 8-14 days ago, case counts have increased by 6.6%, while daily reported deaths have increased by 4.5%. Similar comparative 7-day averages in the USA show a 53.3% increase in daily reported cases and a 37.4% increase in reported deaths.

Impression: The global daily report counted over 700 000 newly confirmed infections in the past 24 hours with over 206.22 million cumulative reported cases and over 4.34 million reported deaths. - Mod.UBA]
